9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What startling command was given to Abraham? What </div><div class="t m2498 x53 h4 y1c7d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">was still left untold? Verse 2. Note 2. </div><div class="t m2b6 x61 h4 y1b90 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m27e3 xc5 h4 y1660 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How long did Abraham wait before obeying? Whom </div><div class="t m7e5 x53 h4 y17bf ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">did he take with him? What did they take with them? </div><div class="t m14e2 x53 h4 y1855 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verse 3. </div><div class="t ma2 x61 h4 y1d5f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m154f xc5 h4 y1d5f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What did Abraham see on the third day of that sad </div><div class="t m21fa x53 h4 y18f2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">journey? Verse 4. </div><div class="t m1cd x61 h4 y152f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m2473 xc h4 y152f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What statement did Abraham make to the young men </div><div class="t m1caf x55 h4 y1e31 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which indicated his faith in God&apos;s promise? Verse 5. </div><div class="t m6a1 x53 h4 y17c3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Note 3. </div><div class="t m1d0 x61 h4 y17c4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m1f9b xc h4 y1e8c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Upon whom did he place the wood? Who carried the fire </div><div class="t m70f x53 h4 y1376 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the knife? Verse 6. </div><div class="t m1d2 x61 h4 y150a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m175b xc h4 y215a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What endearing words now fell from the lips of Isaac? </div><div class="t m1c96 x55 h4 y1ac1 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What question did Isaac ask? Verse 7. </div><div class="t m1d5 x74 h4 y20e0 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m145d xc h4 y1b81 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What prophetic reply did Abraham make? Verse 8. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.00000